Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:40.89,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}巡り逢ったが運の尽き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:48.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}ハラリ　零れ落ちる 言葉　連ねたとて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:55.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}誰もあたしに在る真 触れも出来んじゃろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:58.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}サクラ　舞うが如く　　　　　　　　　　　　　　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:02.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}今生とはおさらば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:09.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}されど親に貰ったこの身が可愛い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:12.91,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}命より重い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:16.74,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}べべ纏い微笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:20.64,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}傷は絶えぬ喧嘩上等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:22.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}覚悟しいや
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:25.77,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}抜いては戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.57,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}刀と鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.53,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}断ち斬るは修羅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:34.28,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}その裂け目に堕ちた夢の
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:38.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}腑は無惨ぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.86,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}相まみえて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.79,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}滾らせる血を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:44.85,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}分け合えるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:49.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}愛し其方　止めを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:52.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}刺さしてくんなまし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:03:01.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}花の盛りが惜しいかえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:40.89,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}与我相遇便是你命已尽数
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:48.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}零零飘落 无从以问
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:55.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}世间何人可碰触我心之真实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:58.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}如樱飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:02.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}永别此生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:09.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}可惜受以父母之身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:12.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}重以生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:16.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}微笑似锦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:20.64,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}伤痛不消 愈战愈勇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:22.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}看透人参吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:25.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}拔起又收回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}刀与剑鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}斩断以之为修罗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:34.28,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}堕落于世间裂痕之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:38.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}结局何以悲惨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.86,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}相与相依
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.79,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}可同流血
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:44.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}亦归途
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:49.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}若爱其身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:52.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}何不与其止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:03:01.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\blur3}只可惜这烂漫花朵
